What we do
Who we serve




What we do

We transform businesses through the art of digitization. Our expertise spans multiple disciplines, providing our clients with software solutions that dramatically drive results and outcomes.












                                    Core Engineering
                                








Developing next-generation software products, shaping strong system foundations, and assuring engineering excellence so your business reaches its maximum potential. 
Learn more »













                                    Advanced Technology
                                








Driving innovation via adaptable, agile architecture that connects people and their devices into the Internet of Things. 
Learn more »













                                    Intelligent Enterprise
                                








Streamlining processes, enabling connected collaboration, and launching enterprise applications through our award-winning global delivery framework. 
Learn more »













                                    Digital Engagement
                                








Helping businesses thrive in the Age of the Customer by implementing omnichannel solutions across all digital platforms. 
Learn more »










Who we serve

The right technology translates business strategies into results. We deliver domain-specific, transformative software solutions that reshape the way you do business.












                                    Financial Services
                                








We address the constant challenge to cope with new regulations and compliance requirements, to reduce costs through operational efficiency and automation, to innovate and transform business processes to meet the age of the customer. EPAM helps  Banks and Financial Institutions meet these challenges across Investment Banking, Retail and Commercial Banking, Wealth Management, Exchanges and Market Data Management.
Learn more »


Case Study »













                                    Travel & Hospitality
                                








We drive innovation for many of the world’s largest and well-known travel companies, serving clients in Airline, Hospitality, Tour and OTA segments globally. We specialize in vertical solutions for Distribution, Loyalty Marketing and provide unique integration capabilities.
Learn more »













                                    Software & Hi-Tech
                                








Our 20 years of history in serving the world’s leading software providers have given us an edge in engineering products. EPAM engineers new products and platforms for  emerging and established software and high-tech companies around the world.
Learn more »













                                    Retail & Distribution
                                








We deliver a complete range of digital commerce and marketing services to a global set of customers across traditional and online retail, manufacturing and distribution segments. We specialize in Digital Strategy, Commerce and Digital Marketing platforms and Analytics and Insights.
Learn more »


Case Study »
White Paper »













                                    Media & Entertainment
                                








We help connect the world of new Media to the increasingly digital audience of today. We serve all major segments from TV and Cable to Publishing. We specialize in Media strategy, TV Everywhere, Digital Distribution and Analytics solutions.
Learn more »


Case Study »













                                    Life Sciences & Healthcare
                                








Our work with leading Life Sciences and Healthcare companies has given us unique insights into the wave of technology-led innovation now moving those industries toward convergence.
Learn more »


Case Study »













                                    Emerging Verticals
                                








Our work in industries, ranging from Energy and Utilities to Telecom and Automotive, enables our customers to push the very edge of technology transformation and drive innovation from within.
Learn more »




















        
